flowRoot.flowPara: It is good to cool the wort as quickly as possible now to get a clearer beer (trub drops out of the suspension). Connect 2 hoses (with clamps) to the copper coil and run water through to drop the temperature until it is at pitching temp (I get it under 30, put the wort in the fermenter and put the fermenter in the fridge to get it down the last 10 C).
